1. *Mrzi* mi se da čekam. (I don't feel like waiting.)
2. Mnogo mi se *mrzi* da radim. (I really don't want to work.)
3. Ne želim da *mrzim* nikoga. (I don't want to hate anyone.)
4. Ona *mrzi* da čuje istinu. (She hates to hear the truth.)
5. *Mrzilo* mu je da promeni. (He was reluctant to change.)